sequenceDiagram
    participant PlatOp as Platform Operator<br/>(rhods-operator)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant TrainerOp as Trainer Operator<br/>8080/TCP metrics<br/>8081/TCP probes
    participant TrainerCtrl as Kubeflow Trainer Controller<br/>(Managed Deployment)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant User as Data Scientist

    Note over PlatOp,TrainerOp: Flow 1: Trainer Component Provisioning

    PlatOp->>K8sAPI: Create Trainer CR (default-trainer)<br/>ManagementState: Managed<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>TrainerOp: Watch notification: Trainer CR created<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    TrainerOp->>K8sAPI: Check dependencies<br/>- JobSet CRD (jobsets.jobset.x-k8s.io)<br/>- JobSetOperator CR (OpenShift)<br/>- OLM OperatorConditions<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>TrainerOp: Dependencies status

    alt Dependencies Available
        TrainerOp->>K8sAPI: Render kustomize manifests<br/>Patch params.env with RELATED_IMAGE_* env vars
        TrainerOp->>K8sAPI: Server-side apply (field owner: trainer-module-controller)<br/>- Upstream Trainer Deployment + RBAC + Webhooks<br/>- 15 ClusterTrainingRuntimes (CUDA/ROCm/CPU)<br/>- 3 ImageStreams (OpenShift only)<br/>- NetworkPolicies, PodMonitors<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>TrainerOp: Resources applied
        TrainerOp->>K8sAPI: Update Trainer CR status<br/>Conditions: Ready=True, ProvisioningSucceeded=True
    else Dependencies Missing
        TrainerOp->>K8sAPI: Update Trainer CR status<br/>Condition: Degraded=True (descriptive error)
        Note over TrainerOp: Requeue after 60 seconds
    end

    Note over User,JobSetCtrl: Flow 2: Distributed Training Job Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob CR<br/>(references ClusterTrainingRuntime)<br/>Auth: User Token (HTTPS 443/TCP)
    K8sAPI-->>TrainerCtrl: Watch notification: TrainJob created
    TrainerCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet<br/>(distributed training workload)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>JobSetCtrl: Watch notification: JobSet created
    JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Jobs and Pods<br/>(training worker pods)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over TrainerOp,K8sAPI: Drift Correction (Continuous)

    K8sAPI-->>TrainerOp: Watch: managed resource modified<br/>(label: platform.opendatahub.io/part-of=trainer)
    TrainerOp->>K8sAPI: Re-apply desired state<br/>(server-side apply)
